long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract Pinterest collections data from the collection page to a Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the collection page.
2️⃣ Click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

🌳 What groups data can I extract using this tool?
Like type, url, board, category, description, domain, grid_title, id, imageUrl, videoUrl, pinner, isRepin, favorite_user_count, repin_count and so on.
